	f oyster specials across our five Edmonds locations: Bar Dojo\, Fire & The
	 Feast\, Market Seafood Eatery\, Salt & Iron\, and SanKai.\n\nFeaturing oy
	sters from Taylor Shellfish and private label wine pairings from The Winem
	akers Reserve. Regular menus available at all locations.\n\nMake it an oys
	ter crawl with our Oyster Fest Punch Card. Each Oyster Fest item ordered e
	arns one punch. Collect three punches across any of the five locations \\(
